{"tid":2247306,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"太古廣場內嗌口號被指違反國安法 二代美國隊長獲准保釋","createTime":"2020-10-17T17:27:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T19:21:52.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3fb1052a50880fba275be2662fb402bf9dc6d84b","tid":2247306,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:27:06.000Z","msg":"反修例示威者梁凌杰去年6月15日於金鐘太古廣場墮樓身亡，有網民前日於事發第16個月在太古廣場發起悼念活動，其間有第二代「美國隊長」之稱的姓馬男子在場高呼「光復香港」、「香港獨立」等口號，其間20多名警員撲出將他包圍，指他涉嫌違反《國安法》拘捕帶署。至今日下午5時左右，第二代「美國隊長」已獲准保釋候查，須於11月中旬向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n前日傍晚6時起，有市民在太古廣場發起悼念活動，紀念去年6月15日在太古廣場墮樓身亡的反修例示威者梁凌杰，有人帶同鮮花到商場外致祭，數十警員於商場內巡視並拉起封鎖線。有第二代美國隊長之稱的姓馬男子在商場內高呼「光復香港」、「香港獨立」等口號，當時有職員提醒他不要在商場展示旗幟，其後20多名警員撲出將他包圍及高舉紫旗，氣氛緊張，警方其後以涉嫌違反《國安法》將他帶走。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201017/OPVGGGXORVGRNABIX2WYJ7ID7E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201017%2FOPVGGGXORVGRNABIX2WYJ7ID7E%2F&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPe8Zsbf427MOg7dSrB3lcR0%3D&h=0ddc6500\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201017%2FOPVGGGXORVGRNABIX2WYJ7ID7E%2F&h=23953a4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201017/OPVGGGXORVGRNABIX2WYJ7ID7E/</a>"},{"pid":"8c00b9d95389b2ef81a65e989b5d0fc12b4c6f79","tid":2247306,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:29:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"657569c24066b99146c59ac451b36253080cc074","tid":2247306,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c00b9d95389b2ef81a65e989b5d0fc12b4c6f79","tid":2247306,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:29:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr